The paper focuses on using deep-learning image processing and machine learning to analyze online advertising images and construct prediction models for ad success. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories, as well as the machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of graph theory, which could also place it in the natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-category.
